Kerryn Slater is the Inspired Spiritual Alchemist on a mission to support you to gain true purpose clarity, heal your body and mind and connect to a joyous life. She’s a fierce advocate for your awakening!

Kerryn loves to learn and has gathered an abundance of tools and expertise, she’s highly qualified and has a wealth of wisdom she shares generously.

Her business, Holistic Essentials Therapy & Consulting has been the channel to reconnect to your wisdom as you learn to trust being supported by the universe’s beautiful energy. 

As a certified Meditation Teacher, Self Discovery Master Coach, Hypnosis Practitioner, Reiki Master Teacher, Theta healer and Thrive Factor Profiler, she’s a wealth of wisdom and inspiration, with an ability to hold space for genuine transformation.

MY LIFE IS PURE TRANSFORMATION

I go where it hurts. Leaving nothing in my life untouched. Exploring every subtle part of what I would call "me". As deep as I can.
This "quest for truth" has brought me pain and suffering along the way. And yet, it has gifted me the greatest joys I could imagine.
It brought me wisdom. Love. Peace. And made me live life in 4K, instead of sticking to the old 480p resolution I've used to experience life in.

Come. Join me in living life fully. See life, taste life, feel life in ultra high definition. And let me hold space for your very own journey of getting there.

With all the love

Koah is an E-RYT 500, YACEP Yoga Alliance registered instructor. Yoga allowed her to tap into her strengths and weaknesses. It constantly reminds her to not force things in all aspects of life. It has given her the opportunity to grow stronger and more flexible in body and mind. Yoga is not about how far you can stretch the body, its about how far you can stretch your mind. It all starts and ends with breath. Without an even breath, the rest is impossible.
